//! Component tests for `zeroclaw props` CLI subcommand.
//!
//! These tests verify that the `props` subcommand is present
//! and its subcommands (list, get, set, init, complete) parse correctly.
//!
//! The `zeroclaw props` CLI was introduced in PR #5165 as a general-purpose
//! config property management system.

